<i>noun</i>: 할미꽃 [할미꼳] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>할미꽃 [할미꼳]</dt><br>
<dd>pasqueflower</dd><br>
<dd>몸 전체에 긴 털이 촘촘히 나 있으며, 4~5월에 자주색 꽃이 줄기 끝에서 밑을 향해 피는 식물.</dd><br>
<dd>A plant with stalks densely covered in long hair, which bears purple flowers facing downward on the end of the stems in April and May.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>